%% Read replicas (scale reads) + sharding by key (scale beyond one node)
flowchart LR
    App[Application]
    App -->|writes| P[(Primary)]
    App -->|reads| R1[(Replica 1)]
    App -->|reads| R2[(Replica 2)]
    P -. async replication .-> R1
    P -. async replication .-> R2
    subgraph Sharding by key range
      S1[(Shard A-H)]
      S2[(Shard I-P)]
      S3[(Shard Q-Z)]
    end
    App -->|route by shard key| S1
    App --> S2
    App --> S3
